    "The waveform amplitude is rescaled byh lm -→ r ν MC md h lm,(14)where M ≡ m 1 + m 2 is the total mass of the binary, and ν ≡ m 1 m 2 (m 1 +m 2) 2 is the symmetric mass ratio (this convention is specific to TEOBPM and e.g.",
